rows.label: tlk70000056_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Auntie Rynea used to tie back Kei's
hair sometimes.

rows.label: tlk70000056_02_msg0002
rows.name:
She knew all sorts of ways to do it!
It was like magic. It really used to
make Kei smile.

rows.label: tlk70000056_02_msg0003
rows.name:
I asked her where she learned it all, but
all she said was touching hair made her
feel like a different person.

rows.label: tlk70000056_02_msg0004
rows.name:
She said she'd teach both of us how to
tie back hair, too... I wonder what
happened to her?
